WEBVTT

00:03:57.640 --> 00:04:02.239
I worked hard there --
I've counted that I worked at 31 places!

00:04:02.240 --> 00:04:06.460
I went to people’s homes to clean, 
wash utensils, did some small events,

00:04:06.460 --> 00:04:08.110
even looked after dogs and cats.

00:04:08.110 --> 00:04:09.110
White folk have problems
very different from ours!

00:04:09.110 --> 00:04:11.400
(Laughter)

00:04:11.400 --> 00:04:13.639
I was working 
with an American chef in a deli.

00:04:13.640 --> 00:04:15.799
He didn’t like me at all;
I don’t know why.

00:04:15.800 --> 00:04:18.800
One night, he was drunk,
and I don't know why he was mad at me.

00:04:18.800 --> 00:04:22.970
He picked up a huge cleaver and with a lot
of force tried to injure my hand.

00:04:23.600 --> 00:04:29.039
I quit the job because he was taking away 
my pride from me, my very own identity,

00:04:29.040 --> 00:04:31.279
he wanted to break me.